WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
Why this post matters

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Most teams read ideas like Workflow decisions for measurable team performance and still miss behavior transfer in the workflow.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Define baseline first, run one experiment, and inspect deltas before scaling.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Start with one workflow checkpoint, one metric, and one weekly review loop.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
The win is practical: fewer rework loops and clearer accountability in live execution.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Ship one focused iteration, review the signal, and sharpen the next cycle.
